Package: cropmonitor
Type: Package
Title: IFPRI cellphone based crop monitoring application
Version: 0.1
Author: Koen Hufkens
Maintainer: Koen Hufkens <koen.hufkens@gmail.com>
Description: The packages allows for easy processing of data collected 
  within a first field trial concerning cellphone based crop monitoring.
  Written with help from Bob Dylan.
